ArcheNomicon refers both to this instance of a Nomicon game, and the system that supports the game.

The underlying system is named xidb, the eXtensible Immutable Document Base.

The vision is that the requirements, source code and binaries that define the System are all Documents in the Vault.

Additionally the policy that governs the operation and ongoing development of the System is the game of ArcheNomicon that is implemented and supported by the System.

The Vault refers to the entire database of Documents.

Documents (capitalized) referes to xidb documents.

The System refers to xidb technology and policy (what the users interact with)


